    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220\u00b0C/ 200\u00b0C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Slice your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into thin discs</p><p>Add the <strong>potato discs</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Roll your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>lemon mayo</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash then remove <strong>leaves</strong> (2 per person!) from your<strong> lettuce</strong>, pat it dry with kitchen paper and set aside</p><p>Chop the <strong>inner core</strong> into quarters, lengthways</p><p>Chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped chives </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) to a bowl with a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>, then add your <strong>lettuce wedges </strong>and toss \u2013 this is your <strong>chive lettuce salad</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>hot dog bun[s]</strong> down the centre, being careful not to cut all the way through to the other side and open it out like a book</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat and add your <strong>sliced hot dog bun[s]</strong>, cut-side down, and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and charred</p><p>Set aside until serving, reserving the pan</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, drain then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through \u2013 these are your <strong>garlic prawns</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>To build your roll, place the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> down the centre of the <strong>toasted hot dog bun[s]</strong></p><p>Top with a spoonful of <strong>lemon mayo</strong>, the <strong>garlic prawns </strong>and the <strong>remaining chopped chives</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>prawn roll[s]</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/prawn-roll-with-crispy-sweet-potatoes-and-chive-gem-salad/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>prawn roll[s] </strong>with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong>, <strong>chive lettuce salad </strong>and <strong>remaining lemon mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
